Welcome to the world of Hero of Legends! Legendary heroes are waiting your summoning.
Now choose your first fellow partner!
Your power will be enhanced by completing quests, and at the same time you can gather more partners. However, completing quests will consume your stamina.
This stands for your stamina. It will be refilled as time goes by, or you can use diamonds to buy more.
Without further ado, click on the QUEST button and enjoy your first fight now!
You are not alone! Every time you start to complete your quest, you can choose a friend or ask a stranger player to help you.
Click GO button, you will move forward to do exploration, during which you might get rewards or have to fight with confront monsters.
The position of hero is the key to every fight. Please learn to adjust your position before your fight.
Now try to move your hero to the front.
When the exploration is done, you will confront the guarding boss. Please get prepared for the fight.
Nice fight! Now give yourself a sonorous name and continue your adventure.
You've already known how to complete quests. Now enjoy your adventure!
Heroes should meet the leader points requirement, your leadership level is crucial for a team.
Click Replace button or Add button to put new heroes into your team.
What you should note here is that every team must have a leader.
For now you can only form one team, but as you level up, you can own several teams.
Try to complete more quests!
Powerful heroes can greatly strengthen your team! You can use diamonds to summon powerful heroes, and it is free for the first time.
You're so lucky! This powerful hero is as sharp as a razor! Let him show his strength in the fight!
Click character portrait to see his attributes.
There are six star levels of heroes. Each level has its corresponding ability.
There are 4 classes of hero, warrior, ranger, mage and priest.
Warrior has the highest HP. Ranger has the fastest speed. Mage can use powerful AOE spells. And Priest can save team members' lives during the fight.
Different classes of heroes have different skills!
Your can try these skills in fight to see their effects.
Collect more powerful heroes to strengthen your team. Good luck!
Heroes of different star levels have different level caps. Strengthening heroes can raise their levels, but you have to pay gold coins.
Upper level heroes will have higher attribute value.
Congratulations! Your hero has been upgraded. Start a fight to see how powerful he has become.
Reaching the level cap means the power of your hero cannot be strengthened, but you can break through the level cap by using certain special materials.
After the breakthrough, the attribute value will be lower. However, your hero will have more room for further growth.
Congratulations! The power of your hero reaches a new level. He will be more powerful in later quests!
Do you want to bind your Facebook account? It will be helpful to get your game account back when you lose it.
Here you can check all the heroes you've got. Their character portrait are lighted. 
Your achievements can win rewards in this interface. Don't miss your chance.
You can receive mails from system and other players, and send mails to other players here.
You can search your friends in this interface, or add other players to your friend list.
Using friend's hero to complete quest can help you gain friend point, which can be used in a lucky draw.
Make as many friends as possible!
In this interface, heroes can be locked for protection.
Elite quests are upgraded normal quests. After completing these quests you will get more rewards and chances to win upper level heroes.
Special quests show up in a certain period of time. Completing these quests to get rare heroes or materials. Players who has great power cannot miss them.
Here you can check the fragments you have collected. Fragments can make up a new hero card.
Congratuations! You've unlocked the 2X Fighting Speed! Try it now!
This type of card will be gained through adventure and is used to enhance heroes. It cannot be used in battle but offers lots of EXP for hero enhancemenct.
You have achieved level-15, congratulations! Now you can find your rival and fight with him in Battle.
Now let’s talk about the rules of Arena. Here is the Heroes Zone, where you can form a specific team to battle in the arena.
Then look at this Enemy Zone. 3 random teams that rank above you can be selected as your opponents.
Next we will talk about the ranking system. Let’s first go into the Ranking page. 
Here we have the Arena Ranking, where you get information about the most powerful Heroes around the world, and also, knowing where you are.
Tap on the Hero you want to know more to check out his team members. 
Let’s take a look at the reward system. Please tap Reward button.
Hero Arena brings you great bonus! You will get a ranking reward if you finish the daily task of 3 battles. The higher you rank, the more you gain.
Ranking updates when you finish a battle, but you can only challenge 3 battles for free per day while you may spend diamonds for more fights. 
3 Battles Completed! Get your reward here or spend diamonds for more chances.
Having an outline of Hero Arena in your mind? Let’s pick your opponents now.
You will have 30 seconds to set up your battle array before the battle starts.
Ready? Fight!
Battle Ends. Check your new ranking and never stop fighting to rank high!
